# Provider hosts the pod is allowed to reach (POSIX extended regex, one per line). These are the
# upstreams the pod's in-process key proxy forwards to. Add a custom provider's host here if you
# configure one. MinIO is NOT listed — the pod reaches it directly on the internal network (see
# NO_PROXY in docker-compose.pod.yml), so it never transits this proxy.
^api\.openai\.com$
^api\.anthropic\.com$
^generativelanguage\.googleapis\.com$
^api\.x\.ai$
